{"tid":699824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［唐姨風暴] 唐詩詠誘騙黃翠如健身","createTime":"2018-06-13T00:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T16:01:03.000Z","uid":82917,"like":130,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"91d1003ee387a6e4278ff60abde1f16a533aad29","tid":699824,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:22:51.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠想同翠如去旅行，但要等蕭正楠放人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/110311_659e8ab4868c58a121f7e70ac206fe4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F110311_659e8ab4868c58a121f7e70ac206fe4e.png&h=ce97b98e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">屍詠與翠如，分鳩同味，好姊妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  </span><br />\n<br />\n藝人黃翠如與好姊妹唐詩詠昨日現身活動，詩詠笑言日前成功誘騙從來不做運動的翠如一齊健身，翠如笑說：「佢約咗我幾年，我發現好多健身器材都冇見過，今日對腳仲係好痛，本來諗住活動前再做運動，但詩詠怕我哋做完行唔到過嚟。我想操到好似田蕊妮咁。」<br />\n<br />\n約埋睇樓<br />\n<br />\n問到會否孖住上翠如男友蕭正楠主持的《美女廚房》？翠如稱有人提議，但她沒答應：「我私下畀佢（蕭正楠）踩同公開畀佢踩係兩回事。」詩詠指每次約對方都要跟蕭正楠爭人：「我哋話一齊去旅行都約咗半年，希望有人肯放佢畀我。（同埋蕭正楠一齊去？）我唔會做電燈膽。」<span style=\"color: red;\">翠如大爆詩詠每次約食飯，都會將現場所有情侶拆開來坐。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正一閪女人黎，唔抵得呀？<br />\n心地差到，冇人要就收檔啦老虔婆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n此外，翠如和詩詠被發現齊齊出現在新開賣的北角柏蔚山樓盤，巿場消息指樓盤入場費要1,300萬元起，呎價超過26,000元。對於約埋睇樓是否想買樓結婚？翠如表示：「完全唔關我事，係陪詩詠睇啫！」<br />\n<br />\n屍詠呀屍詠，<br />\n快啲搵返幾個契哥哥夾埋過返幾棟樓比你揸手囉。<br />\n反正都人老珠黃冇人要，要定幾間做姑婆屋岩架啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2e3a482200f85b4d179477c60ee80cabdaaf05","tid":699824,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adaf86fb3443398bc17f46a4c778a006dd7ad9a7","tid":699824,"uid":82917,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:34:48.000Z","msg":"死58婆 死58婆 死58婆。。。。"},{"pid":"39015911bf2729db11bde334ebe05bbf9e500238","tid":699824,"uid":156795,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠收啦好無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd9ff81f829ed909c5d5be9904a65d303371f5f","tid":699824,"uid":82917,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"39015911bf2729db11bde334ebe05bbf9e500238","tid":699824,"uid":156795,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:36:52.000Z","msg":"唐詩詠收啦好無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:37:32.000Z","msg":"好撚黑心<br />\n拆散哂啲情侶坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa85b8c34ef662ae8c8606cbe4ebc058d6bdc96","tid":699824,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse